description:
Using ALE meta-analyses to assess distinct and common neural self-representation;
Self-face processing relates to bilateral regions but a right hemispheric dominance;
Self-referential judgments relate to CMS, specifically the ACC/SFC;
The ACC and left IFG/insula represent a core aspect of the self. This dataset was automatically imported from the ANIMA <http://anima.modelgui.org/> database. Version: 1
